data.description: This 2 story, 2032 sq ft home can be occupied as a single family or a multi family property! There are many updates on the main level; new gas furnace & a/c, roof (2019), lighting fixture, laminate flooring, remodeled bath, & new interior doors. The free standing stone FP separates the living rm and family rm. There is formal dining room (presently being used as a den) off the eat-in kitchen which boasts lots of  cabinets and sliders to deck w/pergola. There is a 1st floor has a full bath and bedroom. You'll find 2 (or 3) large bedrooms on the 2nd floor as well as a full bath and kitchen. Property is listed as a two family home. So there are options! New garage door installed. Property is  being sold in as is condition.     See A2A remarks
